OL,3,CS4C apologises after report reveals
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviours' at
OL,5,Cbroadcaster
OL,7,FThe Welsh language broadcaster S4C has
OL,8,Fapologised to "those who have had to
OL,9,Ftolerate unacceptable behaviours" in
OL,10,Fthe workplace following a damning
OL,11,Freport into its working environment.
OL,13,FCapital Law, a law firm based in
OL,14,FCardiff, undertook a fact-finding
OL,15,Fexercise into the culture at S4C
OL,16,Ffollowing serious concerns raised by
OL,17,Fthe Broadcasting, Entertainment,
OL,18,FCommunications and Theatre Union
OL,19,F(BECTU) in April this year.
